---
// Minimal About Section
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16 fade-in-up">
      <p class="minimal-subheading mb-4">Who I Am</p>
      <h2 class="minimal-heading mb-6">About Me</h2>
      <p class="minimal-body">
        Application developer and educational technology trainer, passionate about creating intuitive digital solutions and inspiring the next generation through programming and robotics education.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left: Story -->
      <div class="space-y-6 fade-in-up delay-100">
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          As an application developer with expertise in iOS native development and modern web technologies, I build robust and scalable solutions that blend technical excellence with user-centered design. My experience spans from developing optimized interfaces for Apple devices to creating dynamic web applications with Angular.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Beyond development, I'm dedicated to education—teaching programming and educational robotics to students of all ages. Through tools like Scratch, MakeCode, LEGO WeDo, and Minecraft Education, I foster computational thinking, creativity, and problem-solving skills in over 55 students across multiple institutions.
        </p>
        <hr class="minimal-divider">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="minimal-subheading mb-2">Current Focus</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">iOS Development · Educational Technology · Full Stack Applications</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="minimal-subheading mb-2">Location</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Madrid, Spain</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="minimal-subheading mb-2">Availability</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Open for development projects & educational collaborations</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Info cards -->
      <div class="space-y-6 fade-in-up delay-200">
        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Specialties</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="minimal-tag">iOS Development</span>
            <span class="minimal-tag">Web Applications</span>
            <span class="minimal-tag">Educational Robotics</span>
            <span class="minimal-tag">API Integration</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Development Stack</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Swift, Angular, React, REST APIs, Astro, TypeScript</p>
        </div>

        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Educational Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Scratch, MakeCode, LEGO WeDo, Minecraft Education, Visual Programming</p>
        </div>

        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Code-driven, pedagogically-minded, and collaborative. I build scalable solutions while empowering others through technology education and hands-on learning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
